    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7786689d-08a3-405e-8536-728551ff8d2a">
                Mr. Sydney Silverman  (Nelson and Colne)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7786689d-08a3-405e-8536-728551ff8d2a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-05-31/debates/d7c620fa-95b5-476b-8b44-ef4133d571be/WorldFoodSituation#contribution-7786689d-08a3-405e-8536-728551ff8d2a">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">They did not in the right hon. Gentleman's time.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7786689d-08a3-405e-8536-728551ff8d2a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-05-31/debates/d7c620fa-95b5-476b-8b44-ef4133d571be/WorldFoodSituation#contribution-7786689d-08a3-405e-8536-728551ff8d2a">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-7d27a511-a5d6-4be1-a724-ebfe34a06c0c">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-7d27a511-a5d6-4be1-a724-ebfe34a06c0c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-7d27a511-a5d6-4be1-a724-ebfe34a06c0c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7d27a511-a5d6-4be1-a724-ebfe34a06c0c">
                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7d27a511-a5d6-4be1-a724-ebfe34a06c0c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-05-31/debates/d7c620fa-95b5-476b-8b44-ef4133d571be/WorldFoodSituation#contribution-7d27a511-a5d6-4be1-a724-ebfe34a06c0c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I said that in wartime, when there was a general or partial re-construction, it was not thought necessary for Ministers to make statements. But this is surely a matter to cheer the hon. Member whose pacifist tendencies are so well known. We are now at peace, and we are about to celebrate its joys—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7d27a511-a5d6-4be1-a724-ebfe34a06c0c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-05-31/debates/d7c620fa-95b5-476b-8b44-ef4133d571be/WorldFoodSituation#contribution-7d27a511-a5d6-4be1-a724-ebfe34a06c0c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

