                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c3b7cc51-af62-46c0-9cf0-1a62b8681b3b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
