<p class="">How does the hon. Gentleman reconcile that with the specific statement made by the Prime Minister on 7th May, that before the visit it had been agreed with the United States that India should receive 1,400,000 tons?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
